<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>College Creators | Websites for Small Businesses</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f4f8ff;
      color: #102033;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0057ff, #00a2ff);
      color: white;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 38px;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .logo span {
      background: white;
      color: #0057ff;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    header p {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 15px auto 25px;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: white;
      color: #0057ff;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    section {
      padding: 55px 20px;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 34px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #0057ff;
    }

    .about {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 850px;
      margin: auto;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 25px;
      margin-top: 35px;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .card h3 {
      font-size: 26px;
      color: #0057ff;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .price {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }

    .setup {
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    li {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .highlight {
      border: 3px solid #0057ff;
      transform: scale(1.03);
    }

    .contact {
      background: #0057ff;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .contact h2 {
      color: white;
    }

    .contact a {
      color: white;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 25px;
      background: #102033;
      color: white;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="logo">College <span>Creators</span></div>
    <p>Affordable, modern websites built by college students who understand today’s online world and want to help small businesses grow.</p>
    <a href="#pricing" class="btn">View Pricing</a>
  </header>

  <section>
    <h2>Websites Built for Small Businesses</h2>
    <p class="about">
      College Creators helps small businesses get clean, professional, mobile-friendly websites without paying huge agency prices.
      We bring a younger, creative perspective while keeping everything simple, affordable, and focused on helping your business get more customers.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Website Design</h3>
        <p>Custom-looking websites that make your business look professional online.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Mobile Friendly</h3>
        <p>Your website will look good on phones, tablets, and computers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Monthly Support</h3>
        <p>We help keep your site updated so you do not have to figure everything out alone.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="pricing">
    <h2>Pricing</h2>
    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Starter</h3>
        <div class="price">$250/mo</div>
        <div class="setup">$400 setup fee</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Up to 3 pages</li>
          <li>Mobile-friendly design</li>
          <li>Basic updates</li>
          <li>Contact section</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card highlight">
        <h3>Growth</h3>
        <div class="price">$375/mo</div>
        <div class="setup">$650 setup fee</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Up to 5 pages</li>
          <li>Better layout and branding</li>
          <li>Monthly updates</li>
          <li>Service pages</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Premium</h3>
        <div class="price">$550/mo</div>
        <div class="setup">$800 setup fee</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Unlimited pages</li>
          <li>Advanced design</li>
          <li>Priority updates</li>
          <li>Best for growing businesses</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="contact">
      <h2>Ready to Build Your Website?</h2>
      <p>Call or text us today:</p>
      <p style="font-size: 26px; margin: 15px 0;">
        <a href="tel:5088636372">508-863-6372</a>
      </p>
      <p>College Creators — helping small businesses look bigger online.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2026 College Creators. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
